Overview
More options
The meeting focused on developing a backtesting agent using Cloud code and SDK to automate stock market trading. The team discussed the need to transform raw data from Discord into a usable format, including sentiment analysis and technical indicators. They proposed building a backtesting agent that orchestrates multiple sub-agents for training and decision-making. The agent should handle tasks like data collection, transformation, and model training. The goal is to create an autonomous system that can make trades based on historical data and market conditions, with the potential to scale and adapt over time.

